        <li>Ingredients stores the ingredients users will need to cook</li>
        <li>Dietary Restrictions is a table of </li>
        <li>User Recipes is the join table for Users and Recipes with the date the user added a recipe</li>
        <li>Recipe Ingredients is the join table for recipes and ingredients with the needed quantity</li>
    </ul>
    <h3> Specifications </h3>    
    <ul>
        <li>Database administrators will be able to insert and read entities</li>
        <li>Entities will also be able to be edited and deleted</li>
